de.upb.pcm.pms

Interface TimeFrame

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, TemporalCharacterization, UniqueElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TimeFrameImpl

    public interface TimeFrame
extends TemporalCharacterization
    A representation of the model object 'Time Frame'. Interval representing a strict time intervall with start and end times.

    The following features are supported:

    • Start
    • Stop

    See Also:
    PmsPackage.getTimeFrame()
